titleNullable: Oxford Pets Cleaned for EML Tools
subtitleNullable: Dataset for Testing and Debugging Object Detection Pipelines
descriptionNullable: This dataset is a subset of the Oxford Pets dataset (source https://www.robots.ox.ac.uk/~vgg/data/pets/). It contains the two classes cats and dogs. Faulty images have been removed. Annotations for Pascal VOC, Coco, TFRecords and Yolo are included to provide a complete dataset for testing object detection pipelines.
